00:00:15.480 --> 00:00:22.080
Science Hangout. If this is your first time, what is this? It's an open space for the whole

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:27.959
data science community to connect and chat about data science leadership, questions you're

00:00:27.959 --> 00:00:33.799
all facing, and really just what's going on in the world of data science. So we really

00:00:33.799 --> 00:00:38.759
want to create spaces where everybody can participate, and we can hear from everyone.

