Sure. So I do manage a little bit of variety of data scientists. There's some bioinformatician,

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:46.240
genomicists on the team. I have a few data analytics stragglers in there too. But yeah,

00:02:46.240 --> 00:02:50.960
so primarily I manage a team of 16 that's going to be bumping up to 18 right now.

00:02:53.039 --> 00:02:58.000
Their work kind of varies depending on their role and expertise. Some people do ML ops,

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:02.720
ML engineering. There's some data engineers as well on that team that specialize

