don't really change too much. You're just a little bit more hands-off. You have more of a variety of

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:45.679
problems, but the thing that led me to help others is exactly that, right? There's more of an

00:04:45.679 --> 00:04:51.119
opportunity to help develop people, round out some skill sets, identify maybe some weaknesses,

00:04:51.119 --> 00:04:56.160
some strengths where others can actually help one another as well. So that's a little bit of part of

