00:12:09.840 --> 00:12:16.320
an opportunity, continuously looking is, is probably my advice. But a lot of people are

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:21.679
just looking to help others in today's society. So giving them that opportunity, showcasing that

00:12:21.679 --> 00:12:26.880
your firm's really about that, I think will help retain and acquire some of the key talent that

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:36.080
you're looking for. Awesome, thanks. I see, Steve, you asked a question earlier, which I think might

