more Power BI developers than Tableau at this point. But they're not going to be one in the

00:14:19.359 --> 00:14:24.400
same Tableau and you know, Power BI are easy to develop, you know, key visuals for business

00:14:24.400 --> 00:14:30.799
objectives. I would say Python are both of those languages are geared towards understanding what's

00:14:30.799 --> 00:14:35.679
going on with a data set at a given time. So when it comes to present presentation,

00:14:35.679 --> 00:14:41.039
continual integration, dashboards, visualizations, they're great, especially for automation

00:14:41.039 --> 00:14:46.159
initiatives. So we do encourage some of our data scientists to, as you know, be familiar with some

00:14:46.159 --> 00:14:51.200
of those visualization tools, they're very key for business objectives, relaying information to

00:14:51.200 --> 00:14:59.119
