00:18:00.000 --> 00:18:05.119
that they need, understanding where's the initial pain point in development, and just giving them

00:18:05.119 --> 00:18:09.920
the tools, pairing them with someone that may have that skill set. If they don't, that's okay.

00:18:09.920 --> 00:18:13.119
We can guide them and, you know, make sure that they're understanding what they're reading is

